                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The nurse has instructed a client with myasthenia gravis about strategies for self-management at home. The nurse determines a need for further teaching if the client makes which statement?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "a0f7d178f7b728b8bba7ef20ddeca62d",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nMost ongoing treatment for myasthenia gravis is done in outpatient settings, and the client must be aware of the lifestyle changes needed to maintain independence. The client needs to carry medical identification about the presence of the condition. Taking medications an hour before mealtime gives greater muscle strength for chewing and is indicated. The client needs to have portable suction equipment and a portable resuscitation bag available in case of respiratory distress. The client would avoid situations and other factors, including stress, infection, heat, surgery, and alcohol, that could worsen the symptoms.",
                        "id": "37695075b4314854a63c7712fa17fab0",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "b95935c946024accb50fa0448eae7358",
                                "content": "Atropine sulfate"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "7cac663328b945d1ad12e80a531bee92",
                                "content": "Morphine sulfate"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "509574d1443e457e9a619f90779f06d8",
                                "content": "Protamine sulfate"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "1a18bdb52e954d5d96faa91a911fbc94",
                                "content": "Pyridostigmine bromide"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "1",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "b95935c946024accb50fa0448eae7358",
                                    "content": "Atropine sulfate"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "7cac663328b945d1ad12e80a531bee92",
                                    "content": "Morphine sulfate"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
