                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "<p>The nurse has provided instructions to a client with a diagnosis of myasthenia gravis about home care measures. Which client statement indicates the need for further teaching?</p>",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "a0f7d178f7b728b8bba7ef20ddeca62d",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Evaluating 评价",
                        "textAnalysis": "<p>Rationale:</p><p>The client with myasthenia gravis and the client's family need to be taught information about the disease and its treatment. They need to be aware of the side and adverse effects of anticholinesterase medications and corticosteroids and would be taught that timing of anticholinesterase medication is critical. It is important to instruct the client to administer the medication on time to maintain a chemical balance at the neuromuscular junction. If it is not given on time, the client may become too weak to even swallow. Resting after a walk, coughing and deep breathing many times during the day, and calling the primary health care provider when experiencing abdominal cramps and diarrhea indicate a correct understanding of home care instructions to maintain health with this neurological degenerative disease.</p>",
                        "id": "b5ec99c02f27437e92cebab0aac7c059",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "b9444443e2c44884a981239560e53576",
                                "content": "Oxygen and metered-dose inhaler"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "4bb1d6c5d2744a5c80e2dc16c984f562",
                                "content": "Ambu bag and suction equipment"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "67ae194d3be24eb5884b00f48c22b156",
                                "content": "Pulse oximeter and cardiac monitor"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "a5dca9d5cfef48cf974b15f1e721ad6d",
                                "content": "Incentive spirometer and cough pillow"
                            }
                        ],
