                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "A client with myasthenia gravis is having difficulty with airway clearance and difficulty with maintaining an effective breathing pattern. The nurse would keep which most important items available at the client's bedside?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThe client with myasthenia gravis may experience episodes of respiratory distress if excessively fatigued or with development of myasthenic or cholinergic crisis. For this reason, an Ambu bag, intubation tray, and suction equipment need to be available at the bedside.",
                        "id": "b7b21f804ac947c196bb733ac62c75cd",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "a3abe66f2b944ded936f61d8bbe9d04e",
                                "content": "No change in the condition"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "894fdbd2ed874eb6ba5f5a039f9fdc11",
                                "content": "Complaints of muscle spasms"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "7bd3a7ca6b304fec92cccc62e60666b1",
                                "content": "An improvement of the weakness"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "8105b280e7c84132803c95d607741f7c",
                                "content": "A temporary worsening of the condition"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "a3abe66f2b944ded936f61d8bbe9d04e",
                                    "content": "No change in the condition"
                                },
                                {
